%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^MAGENTA%^Trickery Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Masters of mischief, those with the trickery domain relish 
the opportunity to confound their foes.  The domain has a 
wide range of abilities, from concealing oneself to creating 
much confusion in one's enemies.

The trickery domain contains the following spells:
Conceal Alignment (2nd), Befuddle (5th), Confusion (7th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Callamir, The Faceless One

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     